# What `gcloud run deploy --source .` uploads to Cloud Build.
#
# CRITICAL: with no .gcloudignore, gcloud auto-generates one that honors .gitignore. Writing
# this file BY HAND turns that off — so the include below is not decorative. Without it, the
# first `npm install` puts frontend/node_modules in the upload.
#!include:.gitignore

.git
.github

# Built in the image (stage 1), never uploaded.
frontend/dist
frontend/node_modules

# Belt-and-braces only: the ~2.8GB California/ raw data is a SIBLING of this repo, outside the
# build context entirely, so it was never an upload risk. Listed so nobody re-derives that.
California/
